sub_title: Marketing Executive at Veolia Water Technologies | Certified Digital Marketing Professional
summary:
MY PAST
3 ½ years of finance/accounting experience within the travel, beer manufacturing, restaurant management and energy industries. Along the way, I’ve specialized in financial and managerial accounting, data analysis and budgeting together with a bit of project management, sales & marketing. 

MY PRESENT
Currently based in the Netherlands as a Marketing Executive for the water treatment industry focusing on key areas: Project Management, Sales, Trade & Product Marketing & Communications. 

MY FUTURE
I look forward to using the skills learned to prosper and grow with new international experiences.
